data.description: 3/2 Immaculate split-floor retreat in a tranquil community! Your dream home oasis (with french front doors, for easy move in) boasts 2022 heated sq ft and a 2 car garage! Open floor plan with large great room, dining room and living room. Plantation shutters give the area an extra touch. The kitchen is the heart of the home with plenty of counter space for you and your guests to enjoy. Find peace on your screened in patio overlooking your avocado and mango tree in the privately fenced in yard, complete with a shed.  The layout of this home is perfect for creating lasting memories! Generous bedroom/bathroom sizes were not spared when this home was built. Master bathroom features double sinks, garden tub AND walk in shower.    Energy efficient double pane windows. New A/C, with UV light & Water heater from 2020. Low HOA.
